<!doctype html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title><%= title %> • Saporsi Core</title>

  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html, body { height: 100%; }
    body { margin: 0; font-family: Inter, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; }

    .page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(900px 500px at -10% -10%, #e9d5ff 0%, transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(900px 520px at 110% 10%, #fbcfe8 0%, transparent 55%),
        linear-gradient(120deg, #fff9f5 0%, #fff2ea 100%);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr .8fr;
      gap: 0;
    }

    .panel-hero {
      padding: 56px 54px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #7c3aed 0%, #db2777 100%);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .panel-hero::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      width: 420px;
      height: 420px;
      right: -130px;
      top: -120px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,.3), rgba(255,255,255,0) 65%);
    }

    .logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-weight: 700; }
    .logo-badge {
      width: 40px; height: 40px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.22);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.36);
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .panel-hero h1 {
      margin: 26px 0 10px;
      font-size: 42px;
      line-height: 1.08;
      max-width: 12ch;
    }

    .panel-hero p {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 50ch;
      line-height: 1.7;
      opacity: .94;
    }

    .benefits {
      margin-top: 26px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      max-width: 420px;
    }

    .benefit {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.14);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.26);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .panel-form {
      padding: 56px 48px;
      background: transparent;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .panel-form h2 { margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 26px; color: #2c221f; }
    .sub { margin: 0 0 18px; color: #7d6e66; font-size: 14px; }

    .alert {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid #fda4af;
      background: #fff1f2;
      color: #9f1239;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .field { margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .field label { display: block; margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 12px; color: #6a5a53; font-weight: 600; }
    .field input {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid #edd9c9;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 12px 13px;
      font-size: 14px;
      outline: none;
      transition: .2s ease;
      color: #2c221f;
    }

    .field input:focus {
      border-color: #a855f7;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(168, 85, 247, .16);
    }

    .hint { margin: 4px 0 14px; font-size: 12px; color: #8a7a71; }

    .btn {
      width: 100%;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #ec4899 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(139, 92, 246, .26);
      transition: transform .15s ease, filter .15s ease;
    }
    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); filter: brightness(1.03); }
    .btn:active { transform: translateY(0); }

    .foot {
      margin-top: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #87786f;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1000px) {
      .page { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .panel-hero { padding: 24px; }
      .panel-hero h1 { font-size: 30px; max-width: none; }
      .panel-form { padding: 24px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <main class="page">
    <section class="panel-hero">
      <div class="logo">
        <span class="logo-badge">S</span>
        <span>Saporsi Core</span>
      </div>
      <h1>Cozy workspace for smarter vending ops.</h1>
      <p>
        Pantau transaksi, performa machine, dan operasional merchant dalam satu
        dashboard yang clean, nyaman, dan cepat dipakai setiap hari.
      </p>
      <div class="benefits">
        <div class="benefit">Owner-ready dashboard and performance KPIs</div>
        <div class="benefit">Secure payment records and audit trail</div>
        <div class="benefit">Fast daily workflow for admin and merchant</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="panel-form">
      <h2>Sign in</h2>
      <div class="sub">Gunakan akun yang sudah terdaftar</div>

      <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="alert"><%= error %></div>
      <% } %>

      <form method="POST" action="/auth/login">
        <div class="field">
          <label>Email / Username</label>
          <input
            name="identifier"
            placeholder="admin@saporsi.local"
            value="<%= value && value.identifier ? value.identifier : '' %>"
            required
          />
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label>Password</label>
          <input
            type="password"
            name="password"
            placeholder="••••••••"
            required
          />
        </div>

        <div class="hint">Tekan Enter untuk login</div>

        <button class="btn" type="submit">Login</button>

        <div class="foot">
          Saporsi Core © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %><br/>
          Reliable vending operations
        </div>
      </form>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
